features: ✅【Purchase Notes】In order to prevent you from purchasing the wrong model, please refer to the second product picture (whether the printer model is compatible) and the Product Description below before purchasing.
✅【Compatibility】Compatible for Canon MAXIFY MB2050 MB2150 MB2155 MB2350 MB2750 MB2755 MB2300 MB2000
✅【Package Content】 6 ink cartridges Cyan Magenta Yellow: 13ml piece

✅【Pigment Ink】LCL PGI-1500XL ink is pigment ink which has a high concentration and contrast, and is an ink that can draw fine characters clearly without color infiltration. Pigment inks are waterproof and light resistant and do not fade even when outdoors, thus allowing prints to last long enough.
✅【Individual Package】 LCL product is packaged in separate box, suitable for long-term storage, to avoid product damage or ink/toner leakage and other problems.

✅【Strict Testing】All products are tested in three stages: Stage 1 - reliability test of raw materials; Stage 2 - finished product color fidelity test; Stage 3 - strict double test: print testing during the manufacturing phase and final testing before leaving factory.
